    <item>
      <title>马科斯警告中国威胁，称他不是在“戳熊”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/marcos-warns-on-china-threat-says-he-s-not-poking-the-bear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，中国在南海的广泛主权声索对菲律宾的威胁正在加大，但他认为，菲律宾政府在争议地区主张主权的努力并不是要通过“戳熊”来引发冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/marcos-warns-on-china-threat-says-he-s-not-poking-the-bear</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 11:50:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒梅尔表示，拜登和特朗普都不会结束美国的保护主义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/neither-biden-nor-trump-will-end-us-protectionism-le-maire-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，无论谁赢得总统选举，美国的保护主义都会继续下去，并呼吁欧洲在贸易问题上采取强硬立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/neither-biden-nor-trump-will-end-us-protectionism-le-maire-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 11:45:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港通过新保安法案巩固中国控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/hong-kong-passes-local-security-bill-cementing-china-s-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港已迅速将国内安全立法纳入法律，批评人士称，该立法可能会压制公开的经济讨论，并加强对在这个全球金融中心运营的外国机构的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/hong-kong-passes-local-security-bill-cementing-china-s-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 10:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国立法者达成协议，为政府提供资金至 9 月 30 日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/us-lawmakers-reach-deal-to-keep-government-open-through-sept-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在长达六个月的激烈意识形态冲突导致年度支出计划推迟完成后，国会领​​导人和白宫达成了一项握手协议，为美国政府提供资金至 9 月 30 日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-19/us-lawmakers-reach-deal-to-keep-government-open-through-sept-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Mar 2024 01:25:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
